  "texts": [
    "Each box in this ordering lattice represents one of the possible sub-DAGs in a small network with nodes {1, 2, 3, 4}.",
    "The optimal DAG is determined by a depth first search of this lattice.",
    "Starting at the top with the DAG containing all nodes, the search moves down the first blue arrow to sub-DAG {1, 2, 3} with node 4 left behind as the sink node.",
    "The highest scoring parents for node 4 in sub-DAG {1, 2, 3} are determined, in this illustration assumed to be {1, 2} with a score of 4.",
    "The search continues down the blue arrows, determining the highest scoring parents for each local sink node until we reach the bottom sub-DAG on the blue path, {1}."
  ],
